      "key": "goal",
      "location": "workflow/AGENTS.md > Project Structure & Module Organization / Security & Configuration Tips / PM Continuous Maintenance",
      "quote": "`logs/`：运行与审计留痕。... `state/`：运行态数据... 严禁提交密钥... 仅当 `DIALOGUE_RETRO_SWITCH: ON` 时，才自动写入每轮复盘增量。"
    },
    {
      "key": "responsibilities.must[0]",
      "location": "workflow/AGENTS.md > Project Structure & Module Organization",
      "quote": "`docs/workflow/`：需求、门禁和证据矩阵文档，先读这里再改流程。"
    },
    {
      "key": "responsibilities.must[1]",
      "location": "workflow/AGENTS.md > Testing Guidelines",
      "quote": "改动 API/流程时，优先补充 `run_phase0_gate_acceptance.py` 对应 case。"
    },
    {
      "key": "responsibilities.must[2]",
      "location": "workflow/AGENTS.md > Testing Guidelines",
      "quote": "验收结果需落盘到 `logs/runs/`，并在必要时更新 `docs/workflow/验收证据矩阵-Phase0.md`。"
    },
    {
      "key": "responsibilities.must[3]",
      "location": "workflow/AGENTS.md > Architecture & Workflow Notes",
      "quote": "修改 UI 时需同步检查 API 字段兼容性。"
    },
    {
      "key": "responsibilities.must[4]",
      "location": "workflow/AGENTS.md > Security & Configuration Tips",
      "quote": "严禁提交密钥或包含敏感信息的 trace；提交前检查 `logs/` 与 `state/` 新增文件。"
    },
    {
      "key": "responsibilities.must[5]",
      "location": "workflow/AGENTS.md > Security & Configuration Tips",
      "quote": "所有写入路径必须限制在 `agent_search_root` 内，保持 `$root` 越界拦截行为不回退。"
